window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>The ninth and final book in the Realm of Arkon series. </p> <p>The world stands on the edge as the Ancient Gods advance on the Great Forest. An enemy from a past life aims to transform into a Beast and destroy Providence itself....</p> <p>To stop him, all must stake their life on the Scales of Fate. All must make a choice, THE choice. Death in battle or life in slavery. A beautiful demoness' smile or the eternal, infinite Void.</p>"; 
